org.cyclops.cyclopscore.config

Class ConfigProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cyclops.cyclopscore.config.ConfigProperty

  • public final class ConfigProperty
extends java.lang.Object
    A holder class for properties that go inside the config file. Used inside the ConfigHandler for configuring the settings of the IConfigurable. Do no confuse with ConfigurableProperty which is an annotation an is internally used to make new instances of ConfigProperty.
